<ol><li>The light is reflected by the&nbsp;<b>concave mirror</b>.</li><li>Then reflected by the&nbsp;<b>convex mirror</b>&nbsp;into the&nbsp;<b>small hole</b>&nbsp;at the centre of the concave mirror into the&nbsp;<b>eyepiece</b>.</li><li>Refracted by the eyepiece into a&nbsp;<b>parallel beam</b>&nbsp;which enters the viewer's eye.</li></ol>